GOKIT
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Glorten's Dungeon project includes the GoKit plugin under the 
/Assets/Plugins/GoKit that has its own license available in 
the project page https://github.com/prime31/GoKit and included bellow.

For any developers just wanting to use GoKit in their games go right ahead. 
You can use GoKit in any and all games either modified or unmodified. In order 
to keep the spirit of this open source project it is expressly forbid to sell 
or commercially distribute GoKit outside of your games. You can freely use it 
in as many games as you would like but you cannot commercially distribute the 
source code either directly or compiled into a library outside of your game.

Feel free to include a "prime31 inside" logo on your about page, web page, 
splash page or anywhere else your game might show up if you would like.
small or larger or huge.

CN CONTROLS
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Glorten's Dungeon project includes the CN Controls Mobile Joystick and 
Touchpad Components, created by Cyrill Nadezhdin and available under the MIT
license.

GLORTEN'S DUNGEON ASSETS
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Glorten's Dungeon 3D models, animatios and textures under the following
folders: 

/Assets/Animations
/Assets/Models
/Assets/Particles
/Assets/Prefabs
/Assets/Resources
/Assets/Scenes
/Assets/UI/Animations
/Assets/UI/BossFight
/Assets/UI/Textures

excluding logos and the fonts and texts included in the images are 
available under the CC BY 4.0 (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)
license.

GLORTEN'S DUNGEON FX and MUSIC
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Boss fight ambient music has been composed by Albert "hellmer" Gallego 
(https://soundcloud.com/hell_mer) and is available under CC BY-ND 4.0 
(http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nd/4.0/)

ALMENDRA FONT
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The Almendra font .ttf files included in the /Assets/Fonts folder are avilable
under the SIL OPEN FONT LICENSE Version 1.1 included in the 
/Assets/Fonts/OFL.txt file.